data.description: Located on a cul-de-sac in the deed restriction community of Sugarmill Woods. This 3 bed /2 bath / 2 car garage pool home checks all the boxes. The family chef will love the spacious kitchen with plenty of counter space & complete with pantry. Eat in kitchen overlooks the pool & greenbelt that Sugarmill Woods is famous for, no one can build behind your home. Primary suite with lanai access features dual sinks, garden tub & walk in shower. Relax & unwind on the oversized lanai, as you listen to the soothing sounds of the waterfall cascading into the pool. Public sewer & water, well for irrigation. Minutes from boating, shops & restaurants, with convenient access to the Suncoast Parkway. Welcome home.
